  "title": "Assistant Childcare Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Assist the lead teacher in delivering lessons, provide attentive care and guidance to young children, and support the organisation of school activities to create a positive learning environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support the lead teacher in preparing and delivering lesson activities to engage young children effectively</li><li>Provide attentive care and guidance to young children to support their development and well-being</li><li>Assist in planning and organising school activities to enhance the educational experience</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Hold a Fundamentals or Advance Certificate in Early Childhood Care and Education</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate passion for nurturing and educating young children</li><li>Exhibit a positive attitude and collaborate effectively as a team player</li><li>Show commitment to building a long-term career in early childhood education</li><li>Preferably have work experience in a related field</li></ul>",
